text: Noita is the Finnish word for witch and may refer to: *Noita (album), a 2015 album by Korpiklaani *Noita palaa elämään (English: The Witch), a 1952 Finnish horror film *"Noita", a song by 22-Pistepirkko from their 1984 album Piano, rumpu ja kukka *"Noita", a song by Indica from their 2007 album Kadonnut puutarha *Noita (video game), a 2020 action-adventure game by Nolla Games
title: Noita
